This package provides a fully functional Oxid CE demo environment.

Requirements:
- VirtualBox 4.2 or higher
- Vagrant 1.2.2 or higher

Download Links:
Virtualbox
https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads

Vagrant
http://downloads.vagrantup.com/

Installation:

1. Install Vagrant and Virtualbox.
2. Change users/passwords in ./oxid_config/oxid_demo.cfg to your need.
3. Execute 'vagrant up' inside the main directory (where the Vagrantfile reside).
4. Vagrant will now download the required base box, and configure the virtual machine.
5. Change your local hosts file to point your ip to 'www.oxiddemo.de'.
6. Open http://www.oxiddemo.de:8080 in your browser to use your demo shop.
